verbose_text: As shown in Figure XREF_FIG, there was no significant association between performance on either test and with : (1) Digit Span general cognition; (2) logMar letter acuity; or Pelli-Robson contrast sensitivity - although there was a trend towards an association between acuity and performance on the Search task (p = 0.056; r = 0.27).
